OL,3,CMitchum apologises after deodorant
OL,4,Cleaves customers with 'burning armpits'
OL,6,FMitchum has apologised after customers
OL,7,Freported rashes, bumps and burning
OL,8,Flinked to one of its roll-on
OL,9,Fdeodorants.
OL,11,FTikTok users posted videos
OL,12,Fhighlighting redness and irritation
OL,13,Fafter using the brand's 48-hour roll-
OL,14,Fon anti-perspirant and deodorant.
OL,16,FOne person described the sensation
OL,17,Flike "volcanoes erupting" out of their
OL,18,Farmpits, while another said they
OL,19,Fhadn't been able to go running due to
OL,20,Fthe pain.
