OL,3,CMitchum apologises after deodorant
OL,4,Cleaves customers with 'burning armpits'
OL,6,FMany assumed the issue was caused by a
OL,7,Fchange in the product's formula, but
OL,8,FMitchum UK confirmed that, after an
OL,9,Finvestigation, the problem was linked
OL,10,Fto the brand adopting a different
OL,11,Fmanufacturing process.
OL,13,FA select batch of the roll-on sold in
OL,14,Fthe UK, Ireland and South Africa was
OL,15,Fimpacted by the updated method, and
OL,16,Fthe company has now reverted to the
OL,17,Foriginal process.
