OL,3,CMitchum apologises after deodorant
OL,4,Cleaves customers with 'burning armpits'
OL,6,FA Mitchum UK spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Consumer wellbeing is always our
OL,8,Fpriority, and we are truly sorry some
OL,9,Fof our customers have experienced
OL,10,Ftemporary irritation. This is not the
OL,11,Fexperience they expect from us.
OL,13,F"We take this kind of feedback
OL,14,Fextremely seriously and have worked
OL,15,Fhard to investigate the cause.
OL,17,F"We want to reassure there has been no
OL,18,Fchange to the formula of our products,
OL,19,Fbut we have identified a change in the
OL,20,Fmanufacturing process affecting one of
OL,21,Four raw materials."
