OL,3,CMitchum apologises after deodorant
OL,4,Cleaves customers with 'burning armpits'
OL,6,FThe deodorant brand has said it has
OL,7,Fresolved the manufacturing issue and
OL,8,Fis "working to remove the small amount
OL,9,Fof product remaining on shelves."
OL,11,FCustomers experiencing issues have
OL,12,Fbeen urged to contact Mitchum UK's
OL,13,FCustomer Care team.
OL,15,FNo other Mitchum products have been
OL,16,Faffected.
